QUESTION :3

Delete the purchase details of product ‘pen’ in the in_id ‘1006’.


Query:

mysql> delete from invoice_item where pid=102 and inv_id=1006 ;

Query OK, 1 row affected (0.04 sec)

mysql> select * from invoice_item;

+--------+------+----------+
| inv_id | pid  | quantity |
+--------+------+----------+
|   1002 |  102 |        5 |
|   1002 |  104 |        2 |
|   1003 |  103 |        2 |
|   1003 |  102 |        3 |
|   1003 |  101 |        7 |
|   1004 |  106 |       10 |
|   1006 |  101 |        2 |
+--------+------+----------+

