QUESTION :5

Delete all records from STUDENT table.


Query:

mysql> delete from student;

Query OK, 5 rows affected (0.06 sec)

mysql> select * from student;

Empty set (0.00 sec)

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------



QUESTION :6

Delete Invoice details of a particular customer.

Query:

mysql> delete from invoice_item where inv_id=1002;

Query OK, 2 rows affected (0.07 sec)

mysql> select * from invoice_item;

+--------+------+----------+
| inv_id | pid  | quantity |
+--------+------+----------+
|   1003 |  103 |        2 |
|   1003 |  102 |        3 |
|   1003 |  101 |        7 |
|   1004 |  106 |       10 |
|   1006 |  101 |        2 |
+--------+------+----------+


mysql> delete from invoice_master where inv_id=1002;

Query OK, 1 row affected (0.08 sec)

mysql> select * from invoice_master;

+--------+---------+------------+
| inv_id | cust_id | inv_date   |
+--------+---------+------------+
|   1001 |       1 | 2022-01-01 |
|   1003 |       3 | 2021-06-03 |
|   1004 |       3 | 2022-04-04 |
|   1005 |       4 | 2021-03-07 |
|   1006 |       4 | 2021-09-05 |
+--------+---------+------------+

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

QUESTION :7

Delete the first two records of INVOICE_ITEM table its purchase quantity is high.

Query: 

mysql> select * from invoice_item;

+--------+------+----------+
| inv_id | pid  | quantity |
+--------+------+----------+
|   1003 |  103 |        2 |
|   1003 |  102 |        3 |
|   1003 |  101 |        7 |
|   1004 |  106 |       10 |
|   1006 |  101 |        2 |
+--------+------+----------+


mysql> delete from invoice_item order by quantity desc limit 2;

Query OK, 2 rows affected (0.08 sec)

mysql> select * from invoice_item;

+--------+------+----------+
| inv_id | pid  | quantity |
+--------+------+----------+
|   1003 |  103 |        2 |
|   1003 |  102 |        3 |
|   1006 |  101 |        2 |
+--------+------+----------+

